---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Gophy"
  description="Terms of Service for Gophy. Read our terms and conditions."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          By accessing or using Gophy ("Service"), you agree to be bound by these
          Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Gophy is an AI-powered assistant for technical sales professionals.
          The Service provides real-time suggestions during video calls, meeting preparation,
          and automated demo code generation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          You must create an account to use the Service. You are responsible for maintaining
          the confidentiality of your account and for all activities under your account.
          You must be at least 18 years old to use the Service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Record or store meeting content without consent of all participants</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or extract our AI models</li>
          <li>Share your account credentials with others</li>
          <li>Use the Service to harass, abuse, or harm others</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Subscription and Billing</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.1 Free Tier</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The free tier includes 1 meeting with a 30-minute limit. No credit card required.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.2 Paid Subscriptions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Paid subscriptions are billed monthly. You may cancel at any time, and your
          subscription will remain active until the end of the billing period.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">5.3 Refunds</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We offer a 14-day money-back guarantee for first-time subscribers. Contact
          support to request a refund.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The Service, including all content, features, and functionality, is owned by
          Gophy and protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.
          Generated demo code is licensed to you for your use with prospects.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not
          guarantee that AI suggestions will be accurate, complete, or suitable for
          your specific needs. You are responsible for reviewing all suggestions before use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, Gophy shall not be liable for
          any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages resulting
          from your use of the Service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of material
          changes via email or through the Service. Continued use after changes constitutes
          acceptance of the new Terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          For questions about these Terms, contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:legal@garutyunov.com" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">
            legal@garutyunov.com
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
